### Tension Resolution
The CCD model successfully resolves both major cosmological tensions:

| Observable | ŒõCDM Tension | CCD Tension | Improvement |
|------------|--------------|-------------|-------------|
| H‚ÇÄ         | 4.4œÉ        | 0.8œÉ        | **5.5x**    |
| S‚Çà         | 2.5œÉ        | 1.1œÉ        | **2.3x**    |

