```
Model          | œá¬≤/DOF | log(Evidence) | Œîlog(Z)
---------------|--------|---------------|--------
ŒõCDM           | 1.12   | -1228.4      | 0.0
CCD (This Work)| 1.08   | -1222.6      | +5.8
Early DE       | 1.15   | -1234.1      | -5.7
